description: Rogue One Inc. is a diversified holding company in the spirit and hospitality sectors, engages in licensing and marketing beverage products in the Asian markets. It primary focus on the tequila industry. The company serves as a middleman for beverage owners who wanted to get their products into the Asian markets. Human Brands International, Inc. was formerly known as HUMAN Brands Inc. and changed its name to Human Brands International, Inc. in August 2014. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
